- You couldn't make that onions?

499
00:48:30.730 --> 00:48:33.566
Oh. so that's your game.

500
00:48:35.945 --> 00:48:38.947
Professor Wagstaff!

501
00:48:39.366 --> 00:48:42.985
Just call me Quincy.
And later you can call me Quince.

502
00:48:43.413 --> 00:48:46.415
Throw me the lifesaver!

503
00:48:47.335 --> 00:48:49.957
Please hurry. Professor.

504
00:48:58.182 --> 00:49:00.140
39. This is it!

505
