Hello. Yeah. this is McHardie.

506
00:49:12.241 --> 00:49:14.151
So they're coming right over?

507
00:49:14.578 --> 00:49:16.986
OK. we'll take care of them.

508
00:49:17.749 --> 00:49:22.162
Jennings says Baravelli and the dog
catcher are coming to kidnap us

509
00:49:22.588 --> 00:49:25.044
to keep us out of the game.

510
00:49:29.555 --> 00:49:32.592
This is the place.
Now how we gonna catch 'em?

511
00:49:33.227 --> 00:49:36.145
No. that's for flies.
Baseball players catch flies.

512
00:49:36.564 --> 00:49:39.352
We look for football players.
You bring the tools?

513
00:49:39.777 --> 00:49:43.692
You got the shovel. the axe
and the pick? Where's the pick?

514
00:49:44.324 --> 00:49:46.946
No. that's no pick. That's a hog.

515
00:49:47.370 --> 00:49:49.612
Don't you know what a hog is?

516
00:49:50.040 --> 00:49:53.789
Oh. come on. let's get busy.
We gotta kidnap those players.

517
00:49:57.007 --> 00:49:58.632
Mullen und McHardie?

518
00:49:59.051 --> 00:50:02.302
That's us. What can we do for you?
- You got a brother?

519
00:50:02.723 --> 00:50:05.297
No.
- You got a sister? - Yeah.

520
00:50:05.726 --> 00:50:08.265
She's a very sick man.
You better come with us.

521
00:50:08.855 --> 00:50:11.014
What happened to her?

522
00:50:11.442 --> 00:50:13.186
She crash her automobile.

523
00:50:13.612 --> 00:50:17.824
She has no automobile. - Then she fell
off a horse. We drive you there.

524
00:50:18.242 --> 00:50:21.280
You will? I have no sister.

525
00:50:21.705 --> 00:50:24.992
That's alright.
We gotta no car. Come on.

526
00:50:25.418 --> 00:50:28.206
You think
you're gonna take us for a ride?

527
