Get tough with the other one.

532
00:50:52.453 --> 00:50:54.363
Get tough with both of them.

533
00:50:54.831 --> 00:50:56.373
Tougher!

534
00:51:08.640 --> 00:51:11.512
Now you're getting someplace.

535
00:51:16.901 --> 00:51:19.274
You better think of something else.

536
00:51:23.743 --> 00:51:26.413
I'm exhausted. too.

537
00:51:27.414 --> 00:51:30.416
Maybe you fellas got an idea?
- I'll say we do.

538
00:51:30.877 --> 00:51:32.954
Where's that rope. Ed?

539
00:51:33.839 --> 00:51:34.871
Get 'em. Ed!

540
00:51:46.230 --> 00:51:49.397
Hey guys. we'll let you know
how the game comes out.

541
00:51:51.195 --> 00:51:53.318
Now they've kidnapped us!

542
00:51:53.739 --> 00:51:56.860
That's a fix-a fine we're in.
How we gonna get out?

543
00:51:57.286 --> 00:51:59.658
I got an idea. You got a rope?

544
00:52:01.625 --> 00:52:04.959
That's fine. Tie on the bed.
throw the rope out the window.

545
00:52:05.379 --> 00:52:08.334
Tie on the bed.
throw the rope out the window.

546
00:52:10.845 --> 00:52:12.256
Hey!

547
