Don't worry. Mr. Jennings.
everything's working out fine.

553
00:52:40.508 --> 00:52:44.922
Alright. That game's in the bag.
See ya later.

554
00:52:47.141 --> 00:52:50.760
Wonder what the two mugs
are doing up there?

555
00:53:25.148 --> 00:53:29.858
Our little playmates.
just in time for a cup of tea.

556
00:53:30.279 --> 00:53:35.406
We got no cups. See ya after the game.
Come on. Pinky. - No yuh don't!

557
00:53:37.414 --> 00:53:42.326
Take off your coat. Come on.
Off with your shirt.

558
00:53:42.754 --> 00:53:44.628
Quit stallin'.

559
00:53:45.090 --> 00:53:48.045
Now take off your pants.
- I got a date. nothing doing.

560
00:54:06.367 --> 00:54:07.613
You too!

561
00:54:08.203 --> 00:54:10.659
Take that coat off.

562
00:54:12.542 --> 00:54:16.541
Stand over there. you.
Come on. Ed. let's take their clothes.

563
00:54:22.638 --> 00:54:23.468
So.

564
