Darwin's just got a fourth touchdown
and the crowd is going wild.

570
00:55:12.660 --> 00:55:15.662
There seems to be no stopping
Mullen and McHardie.

571
00:55:16.081 --> 00:55:18.074
Two minutes left to play
in the first quarter.

572
00:55:18.501 --> 00:55:22.001
and what a lacing
the Huxley team is getting.

573
00:55:28.013 --> 00:55:30.386
HcHardie has the ball
and he's breaking through.

574
00:55:40.863 --> 00:55:43.189
I guess we made a grand slam.

575
00:56:19.454 --> 00:56:21.162
Pinky. hurry up.

576
00:56:21.582 --> 00:56:24.868
Come on. we still got time to play.

577
00:56:29.467 --> 00:56:33.300
Fine kidnappers you are. The fellas
you kidnapped were here before you.

578
00:56:33.722 --> 00:56:36.759
Look: 12 to nothing.
Fat lot you care.

579
00:56:37.185 --> 00:56:41.350
Know what it means if Huxley loses?
Shame. disgrace. humiliation!

580
00:56:41.774 --> 00:56:45.109
And you're crazy if you don't
