597
00:58:18.606 --> 00:58:22.854
Some football game. I wish
you were here. Instead of me.

598
00:58:23.279 --> 00:58:26.649
Last week. I told you Mrs. Moskowitz
was expecting a blessed event.

599
00:58:27.075 --> 00:58:31.323
Last night Mrs Moskowitz had twins.
OK. Mr. Moskowitz!

600
00:58:32.833 --> 00:58:35.159
Thank you. Professor.
- It was nothing at all.

601
00:58:45.933 --> 00:58:48.685
The boys are back in the field.
they're lined up.

602
00:58:49.103 --> 00:58:51.013
