603
00:58:51.440 --> 00:58:53.397
and there they go!

604
00:59:11.048 --> 00:59:12.163
Pardon me.

605
00:59:26.276 --> 00:59:29.361
That'll teach him to pass a lady
without tipping his hat.

606
00:59:40.169 --> 00:59:44.214
Hey. you wanna get hurt?
We're gonna throw a forward pass.

607
00:59:44.633 --> 00:59:50.887
Signal: 18. 72. forward pass.
eenie. meenie. miney. mo.

608
00:59:56.356 --> 00:59:58.930
Pinky. what are you doing here?

609
01:00:01.696 --> 01:00:04.864
That tackle will cost you 15 yards.

610
01:00:05.284 --> 01:00:08.488
You're supposed to tackle
the man with the ball. understand?

611
01:00:13.545 --> 01:00:15.585
Hey. idiot. where's that ball?

612
01:00:16.006 --> 01:00:19.376
Look. he's got the mumps.
