613
01:00:19.803 --> 01:00:21.131
Give me it.

614
01:00:33.111 --> 01:00:37.940
Ain't deaf over there.
- Signal: 18. 42. 56 and run. Hup!

615
01:00:44.209 --> 01:00:45.668
Bring that back!

616
01:01:08.240 --> 01:01:11.859
Signal: 85. 29. 78. Hup!

617
01:01:23.342 --> 01:01:25.252
Come on. boys.

618
01:01:26.471 --> 01:01:30.221
Jumping anaconda!
Is there a doctor in the stands?

619
01:01:30.643 --> 01:01:34.179
Yes. I'm a doctor.
- How do you like the game. doc?

620
01:01:42.867 --> 01:01:45.359
