There goes the ball.

633
01:03:17.071 --> 01:03:19.645
Go on. Pinky. Make a home run.

634
01:03:28.127 --> 01:03:33.751
Gee. Pinky. you made a touchdown.
Are you tired? That's marvellous.

635
01:04:00.752 --> 01:04:04.418
