- Where's that ball?

636
01:04:07.051 --> 01:04:08.594
Here it is. Come on.

637
01:04:09.012 --> 01:04:11.848
get off that ball.
You're holding up the game.

638
01:04:20.235 --> 01:04:25.776
Signal: Uno. duo. tre. vendi.
this-a time we go left endi.

639
01:04:41.929 --> 01:04:43.757
Nice work. Pinky.

640
01:04:50.148 --> 01:04:53.019
Signal: Hi diddle diddle.
the cat and the fiddle.

641
01:04:53.444 --> 01:04:56.648
this time I think
we go through the middle.

642
01:05:08.338 --> 01:05:10.248
